Janet Berry was president of the Davis Schools Foundation from 2007 to 2008 and led the spring 2008 Dollaraday campaign that helped to avoid cuts in school programs at the time.  She was also campaign manager for the November 2008 Presidential Election/Measure W Measure W school parcel tax campaign in November 2008.  For her work on these projects, she received the A. G. Brinley Award for 2008.
